            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hey, what kind of person...is your<CR>great-great-grandmother?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x169,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Great-great-grandmother? Well, she's very nice and pretty, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x16b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "She's super scary when she's mad."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "It seemed like that, but is she really that scary?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Yeah... I mean, she can freely control time and space."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Huh!? What does that mean!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "It means exactly what it sounds like. She can also transform into, like, dragons and griffons."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "When she caught me being mischievous when I was young, it was crazy cuz she would be breathing fire."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hyeeeh..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "How old was she again? Mom's 33 years old, Grandmother's 56 years old..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Great-grandmother's 71 years old,<CR>and Great-great-grandmother is...<CR>I don't think she's a hundred yet..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I-I can't imagine what kind of person she is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, right? Anyways, she's an amazing witch, and is super pretty, and is the greatest!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "(She must be an amazing person. Although I still don't know what kind of person she is...)"
